      "role": "user",
      "content": "got it. one more thing—i've been seeing some posts online saying that sometimes fat content can get weirdly high in certain batches or between different brands. is there a specific range of fat percentage i should watch out for so he doesn't start getting sluggish or gaining too much weight?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
